Synopsis:

This scripts is used for detecting structural variations in terms
of accumulated variations at one side of the maps (polarity).


Usage:
> AllscrumblePolarity.pl MapsFileinFasta CostFile NameofTempFiles arlem_in_full_path 

Note: NameofTempFile indicated the prefix of temporary files 
      generated. These files store the scrumbled sequences and
      their alignment.  

      arlem_in_full_path: arlem and its path

Destination Directories:
      Output is reported in the directory where sequence file exist.
      The temporary files are stored anywhere according to the given path